            "event": "During his first year of his postgraduate program, he bought a budget laptop to save money, which failed catastrophically two weeks before his thesis submission, forcing him to spend three frantic days recovering data from a repair shop in Koramangala.",
            "lasting_impact": "This experience hardened his conviction that cutting costs on core tools is a false economy, cementing his quality_vs_budget tension and making him consistently prioritize durability over price even when his income is stretched."
