              },
              {
                "age_when": 26,
                "event": "After moving to Chennai for her first full-time job, Priya hired a highly-rated interior freelancer to furnish her studio apartment, but he disappeared after taking half the payment, leaving her with mismatched furniture and a drained savings buffer.",
                "lasting_impact": "She stopped trusting professional or brand claims at face value and now relies almost entirely on peer recommendations from colleagues and online communities she trusts, directly shaping her peer-primary trust orientation."
