            "event": "While setting up his first independent apartment in Bengaluru after joining a data analytics firm, he spent three weeks researching laptops across forums, spec sheets, and Reddit threads before choosing a mid-range ThinkPad over a cheaper option, stretching his first paycheck significantly.",
